agement team across different functions to evaluate and drive internal and external business development opportunities&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Conduct (market) analysis to support crucial management decisions&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;/ul&gt;\n&lt;h4&gt;&lt;br&gt;WHAT WE&#39;RE LOOKING FOR&lt;/h4&gt;\n&lt;ul&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Currently pursuing or already completed a bachelor’s or master’s degree at a top-tier university with excellent grades&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;First professional experience in management consulting, investment banking, venture capital or business development&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Ability to break down complex issues, reduce them to the essential factors and communicate them effectively&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Excellent German and English skills&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;At least three months availability&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;/ul&gt;\n&lt;h4&gt;&lt;br&gt;WHY YOU SHOULD APPLY NOW&lt;/h4&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;Our culture rewards ownership, excellence, and high energy. We care deeply about outcomes and hold each other accountable - we’re here to win and fix one of the largest challenges Europeans face - closing the pension gap and democratising wealth. If this gets you fired up, reach out!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-conclusion&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;We believe it’s our team’s varied identities and backgrounds that make us sharper and stronger. We’re committed to creating an environment where everyone feels respected and has equal opportunity to thrive in 