ting and customer acquisition in a direct-to-consumer and/or app-based business&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;2+ years of relevant experience in a fast-growing technology company&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Analytical mindset&amp;nbsp; - i.e. you have experience with automating reports and you are confident in excel,&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Strong grasp of several digital marketing platforms (i.e. Meta, TikTok, Google Ads, etc.)&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Experimentation experience and mindset with a proven track record of executing A/B tests and translating data into insights&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Entrepreneurial mindset with the ability to succeed in a fast-paced start-up environment&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;You are proficient in English, German is a plus&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;/ul&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHY YOU SHOULD APPLY NOW&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;Our culture rewards ownership, excellence, and high energy. We care deeply about outcomes and hold each other accountable - we’re here to win and fix one of the largest challenges Europeans face - closing the pension gap and democratising wealth. If this gets you fired up, reach out!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-conclusion&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;We believe it’s our team’s varied identities and backgrounds that make us sharper and stronger. We’re committed to creating an environment where everyone feels respected and has equal opportunity to thrive in their careers. For any questions on DEI during the interview process, reach out to your recruitment partner.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;","departments":[{"id":4057653003,"name":"Growth","child_ids":[4057656003,4026478003,4057654003,4064610003,4057655003,4064611003],"parent_id":null}],"offices":[{"id":4024843003,"name":"Berlin","location":"Berlin, Berlin, Germany","child_ids":[],"parent_id":null}]},{"absolute_url":"https://traderepublic.com/en-de/about?jobId=6629263003&gh_jid=6629263003","data_compliance":[{"type":"