ams in preparing and assessing new product initiatives, ensuring Compliance issues are identified and addressed during the product design process&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Advise on relevant regulatory requirements, including MiFID II/MiFIR, MAR/MAD, MiCAR, PSD II, SRD II, EMIR and AML ensuring compliance considerations are embedded early on&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Communication with internal and external stakeholders in all arising questions regarding product compliance&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Provide advice on marketing standards, new campaigns and general marketing approaches for both new and existing products&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Work closely with other departments, in particular Risk, Legal, Finance and People to deliver aligned and consistent input to the product teams.&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;/ul&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHAT WE&#39;RE LOOKING FOR&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;ul&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Successfully completed studies in economics, law or business law or comparable studies&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Ideally, several years of professional experience in the area of investment compliance in auditing or consulting firms, in-depth knowledge of the relevant regulatory and legal requirements, and/or&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Several years of professional experience in the banking or financial services industry&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Knowledge of MiFID II/MiFIR, WpHG, MaComp, MaRisk, MaDepot, MiCAR etc. as well as of other prominent EU regulatory frameworks&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;English is essential; German is highly preferred. Other European languages are beneficial, with Spanish considered a plus.&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;/ul&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHY YOU SHOULD APPLY NOW&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;Our culture rewards ownership, excellence, and high energy. We care deeply about outcomes an