li&gt;\n&lt;/ul&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHY YOU SHOULD APPLY NOW&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;Our culture rewards ownership, excellence, and high energy. We care deeply about outcomes and hold each other accountable - we’re here to win and fix one of the largest challenges Europeans face - closing the pension gap and democratising wealth. If this gets you fired up, reach out!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-conclusion&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;We believe it’s our team’s varied identities and backgrounds that make us sharper and stronger. We’re committed to creating an environment where everyone feels respected and has equal opportunity to thrive in their careers. For any questions on DEI during the interview process, reach out to your recruitment partner.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;","departments":[{"id":4026449003,"name":"Finance","child_ids":[4026455003,4047035003,4047034003,4047036003,4026450003],"parent_id":null}],"offices":[{"id":4024843003,"name":"Berlin","location":"Berlin, Berlin, Germany","child_ids":[],"parent_id":null}]},{"absolute_url":"https://traderepublic.com/en-de/about?jobId=7531005003&gh_jid=7531005003","data_compliance":[{"type":"gdpr","requires_consent":false,"requires_processing_consent":false,"requires_retention_consent":false,"retention_period":null,"demographic_data_consent_applies":false}],"internal_job_id":5679697003,"location":{"name":"Headquarter"},"metadata":null,"id":7531005003,"updated_at":"2026-02-24T10:10:11-05:00","requisition_id":"1150","title":"Senior Internal Auditor","company_name":"Trade Republic","first_published":"2025-12-16T10:24:58-05:00","language":"en","content":"&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Please note that this position is based in Berlin, Germany - relocation support is provided if required.&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;h3&gt;THE BEST WORK OF YOUR CAREER&lt;/h3&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;Trade Republic is the largest savings platform in Europe - we operate in 18 countries, serving +10 million customers who trusted us with over 150B in assets. But we’re striving for more.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;We have a bold mission to empower everyone to build wealth with easy, safe, and free access to financial systems. You will have the opportunity to grow your career by collaborating with a team of outstanding talents and state of the art technology to build a lasting, positive future for millions.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHAT YOU’LL BE DOING&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;ul&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Plan, execute and lead internal audits and support in audit reviews&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Monitor the regulatory environment and assess applicability and action items for Internal Audit and/or the organization&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Identify and evaluate the effectiveness of controls&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Monitor and execute Risk Assessment and audit planning activities&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Support continuous improvement process in audit activities, including software tools, data analytics and process automation/AI&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Review and prepare reports for Trade Republic management and other stakeholders, including identification, definition and communication of suitable relevant actions/measures&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Follow-up of findings raised in previous audits or by external/regulatory auditors to assess remediation status&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Develop and maintain sustainable, trustworthy and effective relationships with key stakeholders in Trade Republic&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Act as an advisor and expert on Banking/Regulatory topics in the Internal Audit team and as contact person for external parties with regard to relevant regulatory topics&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;/ul&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHAT WE&#39;RE LOOKING FOR&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\n&lt;ul&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;You have a minimum of 5 years of experience in internal or external audit&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;You bring ability and curiosity to work in an agile, fast-changing Tech company with a diverse and dynamic team setup and state-of-the-art tools&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;You have in-depth knowledge of German and European financial regulations applying to banks and financial institutions, e.g. particular MaRisk, WpHG, KWG/WpIG, CRR as well as experience and interest in financial products and innovative technology&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;You are passionate about a structured and independent way of working, a very good understanding of processes and expertise in process analysis and description while thinking out of the box&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Problem-solving and driving change by using innovative solutions is as natural to you as paying attention to every detail&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;To sum it up, your excellent written and verbal communication skills in German and English allow you to ease communication with stakeholders, both internally and externally.&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;/ul&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHY YOU SHOULD APPLY NOW&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;Our culture rewards ownership, excellence, and high energy. We care deeply about outcomes and hold each other accountable - we’re here to win and fix one of the largest challenges Europeans face - closing the pension gap and democratising wealth. If this gets you fired up, reach out!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-conclusion&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;We believe it’s our team’s varied identities and backgrounds that make us sharper and stronger. We’re committed to creating an environment where everyone feels respected and has equal opportunity to thrive in their careers. For any questions on DEI during the interview process, reach out to your recruitment partner.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;","departments":[{"id":4026445003,"name":"Internal Audit","child_ids":[],"parent_id":null}],"offices":[{"id":4024843003,"name":"Berlin","location":"Berlin, Berlin, Germany","child_ids":[],"parent_id":null}]},{"absolute_url":"https://traderepublic.com/en-de/about?jobId=7509218003&gh_jid=7509218003","data_compliance":[{"type":"gdpr","requires_consent":false,"requires_processing_consent":false,"requires_retention_consent":false,"retention_period":null,"demographic_data_consent_applies":false}],"internal_job_id":5670870003,"location":{"name":"Headquarter"},"metadata":null,"id":7509218003,"updated_at":"2026-02-24T10:10:11-05:00","requisition_id":"1139","title":"Senior IT Systems Engineer ","company_name":"Trade Republic","first_published":"2025-10-27T07:00:27-04:00","language":"en","content":"&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Please note that this position is based in Berlin, Germany - relocation support is provided if required.&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;h3&gt;THE BEST WORK OF YOUR CAREER&lt;/h3&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;Trade Republic is the largest savings platform in Europe - we operate in 18 countries, serving +10 million customers who trusted us with over 150B in assets. But we’re striving for more.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;We have a bold mission to empower everyone to build wealth with easy, safe, and free access to financial systems. You will have the opportunity to grow your career by collaborating with a team of outstanding talents and state of the art technology to build a lasting, positive future for millions.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;Our &lt;strong&gt;Corporate IT&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt; team&lt;/strong&gt; ensures Trade Republic’s internal infrastructure runs securely and seamlessly, empowering teams across Europe to deliver at scale.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;As a &lt;strong&gt;Senior IT Systems Engineer&lt;/strong&gt;, you’ll combine technical excellence with operational ownership, designing, automating, and maintaining&amp;nbsp;systems that keep the company running.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;THE ROLE&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;We are seeking a Senior IT Systems Engineer to join the CIT Engineering Team at Trade Republic. In&amp;nbsp;this role, you will own the design, implementation, and maintenance of our global enterprise MDM&amp;nbsp;(Jamf Pro) and IAM (Okta) environments, while also administering and optimizing our Atlassian suite&amp;nbsp;(Jira, Jira Service Management) and AWS Workspace infrastructure. You’ll play a key part in&amp;nbsp;automating processes, strengthening security posture, and ensuring scalability across our global&amp;nbsp;environment.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHAT YOU’LL BE DOING&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;● Automate and Secure: Assess, optimize, and automate our Jamf Pro environment, leveraging&amp;nbsp;Bash/Python scripting and APIs for large-scale deployments, patch management, and macOS&amp;nbsp;security compliance.&lt;br&gt;● Build automation pipelines and workflows to improve operational efficiency using CI/CD tools,&amp;nbsp;Git, and GitHub for version control and change management.&lt;br&gt;● Administer and Integrate: Manage and extend our Atlassian Cloud ecosystem (Jira, Jira&amp;nbsp;Service Management) , including custom workflows, automation rules, permissions,&amp;nbsp;notifications, and integrations with external systems.&lt;br&gt;● Documentation: Create and maintain technical documentation, runbooks, and knowledge base&amp;nbsp;articles to ensure operational consistency and cross-team transparency.&lt;br&gt;● Architect and Enhance: Design and implement secure, scalable identity and access&amp;nbsp;management solutions using Okta, including SSO, MFA, and Okta Workflows, integrated with&amp;nbsp;enterprise directories and SaaS platforms.&lt;br&gt;● Develop and optimize AWS Workspaces, EC2, and supporting AWS services to enhance&amp;nbsp;endpoint availability, performance, and security.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHAT WE&#39;RE LOOKING FOR&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;● You have 3-5 years of experience in IT Systems Engineering, Infrastructure Operations, or a&amp;nbsp;related field within a fast-paced, cloud-first environment.&lt;br&gt;● Proven expertise managing Apple ecosystems (macOS, iOS), including Apple Business&amp;nbsp;Manager, Jamf Pro, and endpoint security best practices.&lt;br&gt;● In-depth knowledge of Okta administration (SSO, MFA, lifecycle management, workflows) and&amp;nbsp;Google Workspace integrations.&lt;br&gt;● Experience administering Atlassian Cloud (Jira, Jira Service Management) including project&amp;nbsp;configuration, workflow design, permissions, dashboards, and automation etc.&lt;br&gt;● Solid scripting and automation skills (Python, Bash) with experience integrating systems via&amp;nbsp;APIs.&lt;br&gt;● Familiarity with Git/GitHub for code versioning, CI/CD, and infrastructure-as-code practices.&lt;br&gt;● Strong communication, documentation, and problem-solving skills with the ability to work&amp;nbsp;cross-functionally and mentor junior engineers.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHY YOU SHOULD APPLY NOW&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;We’re a small of 6 but high-impact team that values ownership, excellence, and energy.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;You’ll work in a modern environment where initiative and curiosity are rewarded, whether you’re writing an automation script, tuning a Jamf policy, or crawling under a desk to get a meeting room running again.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;If building world-class Corporate IT operations that power Europe’s leading fintech sounds exciting, we’d love to hear from you.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Our culture rewards ownership, excellence, and high energy. We care deeply about outcomes and hold each other accountable - we’re here to win and fix one of the largest challenges Europeans face - closing the pension gap and democratising wealth. If this gets you fired up, reach out!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-conclusion&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;We believe it’s our team’s varied identities and backgrounds that make us sharper and stronger. We’re committed to creating an environment where everyone feels respected and has equal opportunity to thrive in their careers. For any questions on DEI during the interview process, reach out to your recruitment partner.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;","departments":[{"id":4026464003,"name":"Engineering","child_ids":[4027975003,4027974003,4026472003,4027976003,4057971003,4026469003,4027973003,4047275003],"parent_id":null}],"offices":[{"id":4024843003,"name":"Berlin","location":"Berlin, Berlin, Germany","child_ids":[],"parent_id":null}]},{"absolute_url":"https://traderepublic.com/en-de/about?jobId=7685052003&gh_jid=7685052003","data_compliance":[{"type":"gdpr","requires_consent":false,"requires_processing_consent":false,"requires_retention_consent":false,"retention_period":null,"demographic_data_consent_applies":false}],"internal_job_id":5090423003,"location":{"name":"Berlin; London; Paris"},"metadata":null,"id":7685052003,"updated_at":"2026-04-07T05:07:29-04:00","requisition_id":"1010","title":"Senior Kafka Platform Engineer","company_name":"Trade Republic","first_published":"2026-03-31T08:11:03-04:00","language":"en","content":"&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Please note that these positions are based in London, Berlin or Paris — relocation support is provided if required.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;THE BEST WORK OF YOUR CAREER&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Trade Republic is the largest savings platform in Europe — we operate in 18 countries, serving +10 million customers who trust us with over €150B in assets. But we&#39;re striving for more.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;We have a bold mission to empower everyone to build wealth with easy, safe, and free access to financial systems. You will have the opportunity to grow your career by collaborating with a team of outstanding talents and state of the art technology to build a lasting, positive future for millions.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;ABOUT PLATFORM ENGINEERING&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Platform Engineering is the backbone of Trade Republic&#39;s engineering velocity. Our mission is to build scalable platforms for a Europe-scale bank — serving internal engineers, and building in-house control planes for managing the bank&#39;s infrastructure. We’re a ~50-person Platform team focused on one thing: enabling product engineers to move fast and operate autonomously by default.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;We build self-service platforms, golden paths, and opinionated tooling so that over 400 engineers can ship with confidence. From Kubernetes fleet management and CI/CD to an internal Developer Hub built on Backstage, our work underpins every trade, savings plan, and card payment that flows through the platform.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHAT YOU&#39;LL BE DOING&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Kafka is becoming the central nervous system of Trade Republic — connecting trading, banking, financial crime detection, and more in real time. Today, scaling our Kafka infrastructure to match the pace of the business means too much manual work, too much operational toil, and not enough time building the platform it could be. We are changing that — treating Kafka clusters as fungible shards of a larger resource pool, with a Temporal-backed control plane, Backstage-integrated self-service, and transparent multi-cluster routing that gives product engineers a zero-config experience.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;ul&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Run Kafka at scale:&lt;/strong&gt; Own the reliability and uptime of our Kafka fleet — design for high availability across domains and shards, engineer for resilience, and ensure near-zero downtime across maintenance, upgrades, and failure scenarios.&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Build the streaming platform: &lt;/strong&gt;Design and implement the control plane that makes the multi-cluster platform real — cluster lifecycle automation, topic and ACL provisioning, cross-shard replication, and the self-service interfaces that let product engineers onboard without understanding the infrastructure underneath.&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Make streaming best practices the default: &lt;/strong&gt;Define standards for how product engineers produce and consume — topic design, schema management, consumer group patterns, and reliability practices — and embed them into the platform so the right thing is always the easiest thing.&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Own the platform end to end: &lt;/strong&gt;Participate in the on-call rotation, ensuring full ownership of the systems you build and operate.&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Own the direction: &lt;/strong&gt;Shape the roadmap, drive cross-team initiatives, and align the streaming platform with broader engineering and business goals.&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;/ul&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHAT WE&#39;RE LOOKING FOR&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;ul&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;4+ years of experience in streaming, platform engineering, or a related systems discipline.&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;We are hiring from senior to staff level — whether you are a strong Kafka engineer ready to take on platform ownership, or you have already been leading streaming platform strategy across large engineering organisations, we&#39;d love to hear from you.&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Deep, hands-on Kafka expertise: you have run self-hosted Kafka in production and have strong opinions on cluster architecture, scaling, replication, multi-cluster design, performance tuning, and security.&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Solid backend engineering background — Go is preferred but any strong language is welcome; familiarity with Kotlin/JVM is a plus as you&#39;ll work directly with product teams who rely on it.&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;A track record of turning streaming best practices into opinionated standards that engineering teams actually adopt.&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Cloud-native in your DNA: hands-on with Kubernetes and IaC tooling, running production workloads on AWS or equivalent.&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Ability to drive cross-team initiatives and clearly communicate architectural trade-offs to both engineers and leadership.&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;The ability to work in a flexible hybrid setup, with 2-3 days a week in the office.&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;/ul&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHY YOU SHOULD APPLY NOW&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Our culture rewards ownership, excellence, and high energy. We care deeply about outcomes and hold each other accountable — we&#39;re here to win and fix one of the largest challenges Europeans face — closing the pension gap and democratising wealth. If this gets you fired up, reach out!&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-conclusion&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;We believe it’s our team’s varied identities and backgrounds that make us sharper and stronger. We’re committed to creating an environment where everyone feels respected and has equal opportunity to thrive in their careers. For any questions on DEI during the interview process, reach out to your recruitment partner.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;","departments":[{"id":4027975003,"name":"Site Reliability Engineering","child_ids":[],"parent_id":4026464003}],"offices":[{"id":4024843003,"name":"Berlin","location":"Berlin, Berlin, Germany","child_ids":[],"parent_id":null},{"id":4074610003,"name":"London","location":"London, England, United Kingdom","child_ids":[],"parent_id":null},{"id":4077193003,"name":"Paris ","location":"Paris, Paris, France","child_ids":[],"parent_id":null}]},{"absolute_url":"https://traderepublic.com/en-de/about?jobId=7661373003&gh_jid=7661373003","data_compliance":[{"type":"gdpr","requires_consent":false,"requires_processing_consent":false,"requires_retention_consent":false,"retention_period":null,"demographic_data_consent_applies":false}],"internal_job_id":5730600003,"location":{"name":"Headquarter"},"metadata":null,"id":7661373003,"updated_at":"2026-03-11T10:55:33-04:00","requisition_id":"1200","title":"(Senior) People Partner ","company_name":"Trade Republic","first_published":"2026-03-11T10:53:07-04:00","language":"en","content":"&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Please note that this position is based in Berlin, Germany - relocation support is provided if required.&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;h3&gt;THE BEST WORK OF YOUR CAREER&lt;/h3&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;Trade Republic is the largest savings platform in Europe - we operate in 18 countries, serving 10 million customers who trusted us with over 150B in assets. But we’re striving for more.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;We have a bold mission to empower everyone to build wealth with easy, safe, and free access to financial systems. You will have the opportunity to grow your career by collaborating with a team of outstanding talents and state of the art technology to build a lasting, positive future for millions.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHAT YOU’LL BE DOING&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;The Talent Retention team is dedicated to architecting a sustainable, high-performance culture. Our mandate is to drive organisational effectiveness by designing, validating, and globally scaling strategic People frameworks and products.&amp;nbsp;As a&amp;nbsp;People Partner, you are a critical enabler of this mission. You serve as a trusted advisor to leadership, empowering our managers and leads to cultivate high talent density and design exceptional growth and development opportunities. Ultimately, your contribution will inspire our people to do the best work of their careers at Trade Republic.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;Your responsibilities will include:&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;ul&gt;\n&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Act as a CHRO for your assigned business areas, enabling leadership teams to excel across key dimensions: Engagement, Performance, Feedback, Organisational Design, and Talent Development.&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Design and Drive a Decentralised Talent Strategy, proactively delivering innovative, high-impact solutions that measurably strengthen our unique company culture.&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Contribute to People projects, utilising a rigorous, data-driven approach to develop scalable People solutions that ensure successful change adoption.&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Champion Culture, Engagement, and Performance by continuously diagnosing organisational health and proactively implementing measures that optimise talent output across the board.&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Elevate Leadership and People Capabilities to maximise productivity and sustainably increase talent density within the organisation.&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Establish a Discipline of Continuous Improvement by leveraging People data and feedback loops to enhance the effectiveness and efficiency of our core tools and processes.&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;/ul&gt;\n&lt;h3&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/h3&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHAT WE&#39;RE LOOKING FOR&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;ul&gt;\n&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;4+ years of strategic HR experience (e.g., HR Business Partner, People Programme/Project Manager, or Consultant), with expertise in organisational design, change management, and performance frameworks.&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Proven ability to design and deliver talent strategies and cross-functional initiatives that enhance leadership effectiveness, strengthen engagement, and drive measurable business impact.&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Experience in operating in a fast-paced, high-growth environment, ideally within the Finance or Technology sector, balancing strategic foresight with hands-on delivery.&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Exceptional communication and influencing skills, able to build trust and alignment across leadership teams and diverse stakeholder groups.&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Data-driven mindset: adept at diagnosing organisational health, translating People insights into actionable, scalable solutions.&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Knowledge of German labour law is a plus.&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;/ul&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHY YOU SHOULD APPLY NOW&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;Our culture rewards ownership, excellence, and high energy. We care deeply about outcomes and hold each other accountable - we’re here to win and fix one of the largest challenges Europeans face - closing the pension gap and democratising wealth. If this gets you fired up, reach out!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-conclusion&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;We believe it’s our team’s varied identities and backgrounds that make us sharper and stronger. We’re committed to creating an environment where everyone feels respected and has equal opportunity to thrive in their careers. For any questions on DEI during the interview process, reach out to your recruitment partner.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;","departments":[{"id":4026444003,"name":"People","child_ids":[4047037003,4047041003,4047044003,4047045003],"parent_id":null}],"offices":[{"id":4024843003,"name":"Berlin","location":"Berlin, Berlin, Germany","child_ids":[],"parent_id":null}]},{"absolute_url":"https://traderepublic.com/en-de/about?jobId=7541899003&gh_jid=7541899003","data_compliance":[{"type":"gdpr","requires_consent":false,"requires_processing_consent":false,"requires_retention_consent":false,"retention_period":null,"demographic_data_consent_applies":false}],"internal_job_id":5090423003,"location":{"name":"Berlin; London; Paris"},"metadata":null,"id":7541899003,"updated_at":"2026-03-31T12:24:05-04:00","requisition_id":"1010","title":"Senior Platform Engineer – Developer Experience","company_name":"Trade Republic","first_published":"2025-11-27T12:11:40-05:00","language":"en","content":"&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Please note that this position is based in Berlin — relocation support is provided if required.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;THE BEST WORK OF YOUR CAREER &lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;Trade Republic is the largest savings platform in Europe - we operate in 18 countries, serving +10 million customers who trusted us with over €150B in assets. But we’re striving for more.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;We have a bold mission to empower everyone to build wealth with easy, safe, and free access to financial systems. You will have the opportunity to grow your career by collaborating with a team of outstanding talents and state of the art technology to build a lasting, positive future for millions.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHAT YOU’LL BE DOING&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;Trade Republic is known for shipping fast and strong, and at the core of this is Platform Engineering providing robust and scalable self-service platforms to enable our product engineers to deliver. Moving into the direction of golden paths, self service, and autonomy. We encapsulate complexity and deliver scalable solutions that empower millions of users to invest, trade, and save billions of euros.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;ul&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Build best-in-class CI/CD:&lt;/strong&gt; make sure that developers can always build and deploy quickly, while making sure that the changes meet our high quality standards.&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Accelerate development speed: &lt;/strong&gt;automate mundane repeatable tasks so engineers can focus on what really matters.&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Own the platform:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;Shape the roadmap end-to-end - work with product managers to understand user needs, balance cost, latency, and developer experience, pick the right tech, and clearly explain trade-offs to leadership.&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;/ul&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHAT WE&#39;RE LOOKING FOR&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;ul&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Experience working on infrastructure or platform services.&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Hands-on with CI/CD, Docker, Kubernetes, Linux, and programming.&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with GitHub Actions, AWS, and Terraform.&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Passion for simplifying day-to-day lives of developers.&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Passion for improving productivity with AI.&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;/ul&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;The toolbox we use: GitHub Actions, ArgoCD, Backstage, Claude, Cursor, Copilot, Go, Kubernetes (EKS), AWS, Terraform, Prometheus, Loki, Grafana. Experience with every single item is not required - bring your strengths and curiosity.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHY YOU SHOULD APPLY NOW&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;Our culture rewards ownership, excellence, and high energy. We care deeply about outcomes and hold each other accountable - we’re here to win and fix one of the largest challenges Europeans face - closing the pension gap and democratising wealth. If this gets you fired up, reach out!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-conclusion&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;We believe it’s our team’s varied identities and backgrounds that make us sharper and stronger. We’re committed to creating an environment where everyone feels respected and has equal opportunity to thrive in their careers. For any questions on DEI during the interview process, reach out to your recruitment partner.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;","departments":[{"id":4027975003,"name":"Site Reliability Engineering","child_ids":[],"parent_id":4026464003}],"offices":[{"id":4024843003,"name":"Berlin","location":"Berlin, Berlin, Germany","child_ids":[],"parent_id":null},{"id":4074610003,"name":"London","location":"London, England, United Kingdom","child_ids":[],"parent_id":null},{"id":4077193003,"name":"Paris ","location":"Paris, Paris, France","child_ids":[],"parent_id":null}]},{"absolute_url":"https://traderepublic.com/en-de/about?jobId=6673504003&gh_jid=6673504003","data_compliance":[{"type":"gdpr","requires_consent":false,"requires_processing_consent":false,"requires_retention_consent":false,"retention_period":null,"demographic_data_consent_applies":false}],"internal_job_id":5090423003,"location":{"name":"Berlin; London; Paris"},"metadata":null,"id":6673504003,"updated_at":"2026-03-31T10:16:12-04:00","requisition_id":"1010","title":"(Senior) Platform Engineer (Go)","company_name":"Trade Republic","first_published":"2025-08-06T12:18:56-04:00","language":"en","content":"&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Please note that this position is based in Berlin, London or Paris — relocation support is provided if required.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;THE BEST WORK OF YOUR CAREER &lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;Trade Republic is the largest savings platform in Europe - we operate in 18 countries, serving +10 million customers who trusted us with over €150B in assets. But we’re striving for more. &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;We have a bold mission to empower everyone to build wealth with easy, safe, and free access to financial systems. You will have the opportunity to grow your career by collaborating with a team of outstanding talents and state of the art technology to build a lasting, positive future for millions. &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHAT YOU’LL BE DOING&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Trade Republic is known for shipping fast and strong, and at the core of this is Platform Engineering providing robust and scalable self-service platforms to enable our product engineers to deliver. Moving into the direction of golden paths, self service, and autonomy. We encapsulate complexity and deliver scalable solutions that empower millions of users to invest, trade, and save billions of euros.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;ul&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Build the platform:&lt;/strong&gt; Build in-house provisioning and lifecycle management services in Go—from just-in-time provisioning to hands-off retirement—while integrating directly with underlying infrastructure endpoints and surfacing golden-path templates in our IDP.&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Accelerate developer feedback loops: &lt;/strong&gt;Empower teams to spin up production services in minutes, instrument key developer metrics, and channel those insights back into the platform—cutting cycle times and enabling product engineers to ship great features faster.&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Engineer for resilience at scale: &lt;/strong&gt;Define and monitor SLOs, burn-rates, and error budgets for every platform service. Continuously improve our platform product through functional and non functional testing. Lead blameless post-incident reviews and automate safety guardrails.&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Own the platform: &lt;/strong&gt;Shape the roadmap end-to-end—work with product managers to understand user needs, balance cost, latency, and developer experience, pick the right tech, and clearly explain trade-offs to leadership.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;/ul&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHAT WE&#39;RE LOOKING FOR&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;ul&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;3+ years building backend or platform services in Go.&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Cloud-native in your DNA: hands-on with Kubernetes, Helm, Terraform, and experienced running production workloads on AWS, GCP, or another public cloud.&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;A passion for designing simple APIs for complex infrastructure.&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Proven ability to make distributed systems reliable under real‑world traffic.&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Demonstrated ability to turn best practices into opinionated “paved roads” that make doing the right thing effortless.&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Clear, concise English communication.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;/ul&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;The toolbox we use (and you probably know): Go, Kubernetes (EKS), Karpenter, ArgoCD, AWS, Terraform, Backstage, GitHub Actions, Prometheus, Loki, Grafana. Experience with every single item is not required—bring your strengths and curiosity.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHY YOU SHOULD APPLY NOW&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;Our culture rewards ownership, excellence, and high energy. We care deeply about outcomes and hold each other accountable - we’re here to win and fix one of the largest challenges Europeans face - closing the pension gap and democratising wealth. If this gets you fired up, reach out!&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-conclusion&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;We believe it’s our team’s varied identities and backgrounds that make us sharper and stronger. We’re committed to creating an environment where everyone feels respected and has equal opportunity to thrive in their careers. For any questions on DEI during the interview process, reach out to your recruitment partner.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;","departments":[{"id":4027975003,"name":"Site Reliability Engineering","child_ids":[],"parent_id":4026464003}],"offices":[{"id":4024843003,"name":"Berlin","location":"Berlin, Berlin, Germany","child_ids":[],"parent_id":null},{"id":4074610003,"name":"London","location":"London, England, United Kingdom","child_ids":[],"parent_id":null},{"id":4077193003,"name":"Paris ","location":"Paris, Paris, France","child_ids":[],"parent_id":null}]},{"absolute_url":"https://traderepublic.com/en-de/about?jobId=7685049003&gh_jid=7685049003","data_compliance":[{"type":"gdpr","requires_consent":false,"requires_processing_consent":false,"requires_retention_consent":false,"retention_period":null,"demographic_data_consent_applies":false}],"internal_job_id":5090423003,"location":{"name":"Berlin; London; Paris"},"metadata":null,"id":7685049003,"updated_at":"2026-04-07T05:07:54-04:00","requisition_id":"1010","title":"Senior PostgreSQL Platform Engineer","company_name":"Trade Republic","first_published":"2026-03-31T08:06:21-04:00","language":"en","content":"&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Please note that these positions are based in London, Berlin or Paris — relocation support is provided if required.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;THE BEST WORK OF YOUR CAREER&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Trade Republic is the largest savings platform in Europe — we operate in 18 countries, serving +10 million customers who trust us with over €150B in assets. But we&#39;re striving for more.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;We have a bold mission to empower everyone to build wealth with easy, safe, and free access to financial systems. You will have the opportunity to grow your career by collaborating with a team of outstanding talents and state of the art technology to build a lasting, positive future for millions.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;ABOUT PLATFORM ENGINEERING&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Platform Engineering is the backbone of Trade Republic&#39;s engineering velocity. Our mission is to build scalable platforms for a Europe-scale bank — serving internal engineers, and building in-house control planes for managing the bank&#39;s infrastructure. We’re a ~50-person Platform team focused on one thing: enabling product engineers to move fast and operate autonomously by default.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;We build self-service platforms, golden paths, and opinionated tooling so that over 400 engineers can ship with confidence. From Kubernetes fleet management and CI/CD to an internal Developer Hub built on Backstage, our work underpins every trade, savings plan, and card payment that flows through the platform.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHAT YOU&#39;LL BE DOING&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Our database platform is foundational to how Trade Republic works — every trade, savings plan, and card payment touches it. Today, much of our database operations are handled manually or through basic automation. You will change that: building the platform layer that makes PostgreSQL operations self-service, automated, and reliable by default.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;ul&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Run PostgreSQL at scale: &lt;/strong&gt;Own the reliability and uptime of our PostgreSQL clusters — design for high availability, engineer for resilience, and ensure near-zero downtime across maintenance, upgrades, and failure scenarios.&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Build the database platform:&lt;/strong&gt; Automate the full operational lifecycle — provisioning, configuration, upgrades, scaling, and backup — turning manual database operations into self-service workflows that run without human intervention.&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Make best practices the default:&lt;/strong&gt; Define database standards — schema design, connection management, query patterns, reliability — and embed them into the platform so the right thing is always the easiest thing.&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Own the platform end to end:&lt;/strong&gt; Participate in the on-call rotation, ensuring full ownership of the systems you build and operate.&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Own the direction: &lt;/strong&gt;Shape the roadmap, drive cross-team initiatives, and align the database platform with broader engineering and business goals.&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;/ul&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHAT WE&#39;RE LOOKING FOR&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;ul&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;4+ years of experience in database engineering, platform engineering, or a related systems discipline.&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;We are hiring from senior to staff level — whether you are a strong Postgres engineer ready to take on platform ownership, or you have already been leading database platform strategy across large engineering organisations, we&#39;d love to hear from you.&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Deep, hands-on PostgreSQL expertise: strong opinions on replication, sharding, backup strategies, upgrades, and security. Hands-on experience with Postgres automation and lifecycle tooling is required.&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Solid backend engineering background — Go is preferred but any strong language is welcome; familiarity with Kotlin/JVM is a plus as you&#39;ll work directly with product teams who rely on it.&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;A track record of turning database best practices into opinionated standards that engineering teams actually adopt.&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Cloud-native in your DNA: hands-on with Kubernetes and IaC tooling, running production workloads on AWS or equivalent.&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Ability to drive cross-team initiatives and clearly communicate architectural trade-offs to both engineers and leadership.&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;The ability to work in a flexible hybrid setup, with 2-3 days a week in the office.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;/ul&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHY YOU SHOULD APPLY NOW&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Our culture rewards ownership, excellence, and high energy. We care deeply about outcomes and hold each other accountable — we&#39;re here to win and fix one of the largest challenges Europeans face — closing the pension gap and democratising wealth. If this gets you fired up, reach out!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-conclusion&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;We believe it’s our team’s varied identities and backgrounds that make us sharper and stronger. We’re committed to creating an environment where everyone feels respected and has equal opportunity to thrive in their careers. For any questions on DEI during the interview process, reach out to your recruitment partner.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;","departments":[{"id":4027975003,"name":"Site Reliability Engineering","child_ids":[],"parent_id":4026464003}],"offices":[{"id":4024843003,"name":"Berlin","location":"Berlin, Berlin, Germany","child_ids":[],"parent_id":null},{"id":4074610003,"name":"London","location":"London, England, United Kingdom","child_ids":[],"parent_id":null},{"id":4077193003,"name":"Paris ","location":"Paris, Paris, France","child_ids":[],"parent_id":null}]},{"absolute_url":"https://traderepublic.com/en-de/about?jobId=5207557003&gh_jid=5207557003","data_compliance":[{"type":"gdpr","requires_consent":false,"requires_processing_consent":false,"requires_retention_consent":false,"retention_period":null,"demographic_data_consent_applies":false}],"internal_job_id":4635924003,"location":{"name":"Headquarter"},"metadata":null,"id":5207557003,"updated_at":"2026-02-24T10:10:11-05:00","requisition_id":"626","title":"Senior Product Designer (Mobile)","company_name":"Trade Republic","first_published":"2022-07-05T03:10:57-04:00","language":"en","content":"&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Please note that the position will either be based in London or Berlin, depending on your availability.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;h4&gt;THE BEST WORK OF YOUR CAREER&lt;/h4&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;Trade Republic is the largest savings platform in Europe - we operate in 18 countries, serving +10 million customers who trusted us with over 150B in assets. But we’re striving for more.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;We have a bold mission to empower everyone to build wealth with easy, safe, and free access to financial systems. You will have the opportunity to grow your career by collaborating with a team of outstanding talents and state of the art technology to build a lasting, positive future for millions.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;h4&gt;WHAT YOU&#39;LL BE DOING&lt;/h4&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;We are looking to complement our team of Designers in Wealth.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;ul&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt; You will be responsible for an end-to-end problem space, &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;bringing vision and deliver design solutions from initial concept through shipping and beyond&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Help to create alignment with product and engineering on priorities leading to product design and execution&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Partner closely with other Designers, Product Managers, Engineers and Data Analysts to deliver high quality experiences for different user personas&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Work closely with design leadership across different problem spaces at Trade Republic to improve our design process, operations and practices&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;/ul&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;h4&gt;WHAT WE&#39;RE LOOKING FOR&lt;/h4&gt;\n&lt;ul&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;6+ years of professional experience as a Product Designer building, prototyping, and continually evolving digital products from ideation to implementation, specifically in mobile applications&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;A portfolio that showcases love for the craft and proficiency in problem solving, interaction design, desktop/mobile user interfaces, prototyping and a strong aesthetic sense&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Strong product thinking with the ability to develop product goals, identify opportunities, and make decisions based on people and business needs &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Nice to have: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Experience designing financial products, specially wealth, trading and/or crypto.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;/ul&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;h4&gt;WHY YOU SHOULD APPLY NOW&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;Our culture rewards ownership, excellence, and high energy. We care deeply about outcomes and hold each other accountable - we’re here to win and fix one of the largest challenges Europeans face - closing the pension gap and democratising wealth. If this gets you fired up, reach out!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-conclusion&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;We believe it’s our team’s varied identities and backgrounds that make us sharper and stronger. We’re committed to creating an environment where everyone feels respected and has equal opportunity to thrive in their careers. For any questions on DEI during the interview process, reach out to your recruitment partner.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;","departments":[{"id":4027979003,"name":"Product Design","child_ids":[],"parent_id":4027963003}],"offices":[{"id":4024843003,"name":"Berlin","location":"Berlin, Berlin, Germany","child_ids":[],"parent_id":null}]},{"absolute_url":"https://traderepublic.com/en-de/about?jobId=6683716003&gh_jid=6683716003","data_compliance":[{"type":"gdpr","requires_consent":false,"requires_processing_consent":false,"requires_retention_consent":false,"retention_period":null,"demographic_data_consent_applies":false}],"internal_job_id":5179204003,"location":{"name":"Berlin; London"},"metadata":null,"id":6683716003,"updated_at":"2026-02-24T10:10:11-05:00","requisition_id":"1044","title":"Senior Security Engineer  - Application Security ","company_name":"Trade Republic","first_published":"2025-08-15T10:03:04-04:00","language":"en","content":"&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Please note that this position is based in Berlin or London.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;h4&gt;THE BEST WORK OF YOUR CAREER&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;Trade Republic is the largest savings platform in Europe - we operate in 17 countries, serving +8 million customers who trusted us with over 100B in assets. But we’re striving for more.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;We have a bold mission to empower everyone to build wealth with easy, safe, and free access to financial systems. You will have the opportunity to grow your career by collaborating with a team of outstanding talents and state of the art technology to build a lasting, positive future for millions.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;h4&gt;WHAT YOU&#39;LL BE DOING&lt;/h4&gt;\n&lt;div class=&quot;p-rich_text_section&quot;&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;As a Senior Security Engineer in our Application Security team, you&#39;ll safeguard Trade Republic&#39;s applications and development lifecycle through proactive security integration and engineering excellence. Your responsibilities include:&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;ul class=&quot;p-rich_text_list p-rich_text_list__bullet p-rich_text_list--nested&quot; data-stringify-type=&quot;unordered-list&quot; data-list-tree=&quot;true&quot; data-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Partner with engineering teams to embed security into the software development lifecycle from design to deployment;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Conduct security code reviews, threat modeling sessions, and architecture reviews for critical applications and services;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Design and implement SAST, DAST, and SCA solutions to identify vulnerabilities early in the development process;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Build and maintain application security testing automation within CI/CD pipelines;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Develop secure coding standards, security libraries, and reusable security components for engineering teams;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Perform penetration testing and vulnerability assessments of web applications, APIs, and mobile applications;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Triage, prioritise, and remediate application vulnerabilities working closely with development teams;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Create security champions program and provide security training to engineering teams;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Research emerging application security threats and integrate defensive measures into the security architecture;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Contribute to bug bounty program management and coordinate with external security researchers&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;/ul&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;h4&gt;WHAT WE&#39;RE LOOKING FOR&lt;/h4&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Core Experience&lt;/strong&gt;:&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;ul&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;5+ years as a Security Engineer with 4+ years focused on application security&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Deep understanding of web application security (OWASP Top 10, API security, authentication/authorization)&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Hands-on experience with security testing tools (Burp Suite, OWASP ZAP, Semgrep, etc.)&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Strong programming skills in modern languages (Python, Java, Kotlin, Go, or JavaScript)&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Experience integrating security tooling into CI/CD pipelines (GitHub Actions, GitLab CI, Jenkins)&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Expertise in secure architecture patterns for microservices, APIs, and distributed systems&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Solid understanding of cryptography, secure session management, and identity/access management&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Hands-on experience with security testing of cryptocurrency/blockchain infrastructure and applications is a major bonus&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Experience with mobile application security (iOS/Android)&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Knowledge of compliance frameworks (PCI-DSS, GDPR, MaRisk) is advantageous&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Excellent communication skills to translate security concepts for engineering audience&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;/ul&gt;\n&lt;h4&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/h4&gt;\n&lt;h4&gt;WHY YOU SHOULD APPLY NOW&lt;/h4&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;Our culture rewards ownership, excellence, and high energy. We care deeply about outcomes and hold each other accountable - we’re here to win and fix one of the largest challenges Europeans face - closing the pension gap and democratising wealth. If this gets you fired up, reach out!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-conclusion&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;We believe it’s our team’s varied identities and backgrounds that make us sharper and stronger. We’re committed to creating an environment where everyone feels respected and has equal opportunity to thrive in their careers. For any questions on DEI during the interview process, reach out to your recruitment partner.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;","departments":[{"id":4029831003,"name":"Information Security","child_ids":[],"parent_id":null}],"offices":[{"id":4024843003,"name":"Berlin","location":"Berlin, Berlin, Germany","child_ids":[],"parent_id":null}]},{"absolute_url":"https://traderepublic.com/en-de/about?jobId=6611355003&gh_jid=6611355003","data_compliance":[{"type":"gdpr","requires_consent":false,"requires_processing_consent":false,"requires_retention_consent":false,"retention_period":null,"demographic_data_consent_applies":false}],"internal_job_id":5179204003,"location":{"name":"Berlin; London"},"metadata":null,"id":6611355003,"updated_at":"2026-02-24T10:10:11-05:00","requisition_id":"1044","title":"Senior Security Engineer  - Cloud Security ","company_name":"Trade Republic","first_published":"2025-06-16T09:20:14-04:00","language":"en","content":"&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Please note that this position is based in Berlin or London.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;h4&gt;THE BEST WORK OF YOUR CAREER&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;Trade Republic is the largest savings platform in Europe - we operate in 17 countries, serving +8 million customers who trusted us with over 100B in assets. But we’re striving for more.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;We have a bold mission to empower everyone to build wealth with easy, safe, and free access to financial systems. You will have the opportunity to grow your career by collaborating with a team of outstanding talents and state of the art technology to build a lasting, positive future for millions.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;h4&gt;WHAT YOU&#39;LL BE DOING&lt;/h4&gt;\n&lt;div class=&quot;p-rich_text_section&quot;&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;As a Senior Security Engineer in our Cloud Security team, you&#39;ll architect and maintain secure cloud infrastructure that protects Trade Republic&#39;s critical systems and customer data. Your responsibilities include:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;ul class=&quot;p-rich_text_list p-rich_text_list__bullet p-rich_text_list--nested&quot; data-stringify-type=&quot;unordered-list&quot; data-list-tree=&quot;true&quot; data-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Design and implement security controls for cloud infrastructure across AWS environments;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Build and maintain Infrastructure as Code (IaC) security standards and automated compliance validation;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Develop cloud security automation using Terraform, CloudFormation, and Python to enforce security baselines;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Implement and optimise Cloud Security Posture Management (CSPM) solutions and remediation workflows;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Architect secure network segmentation, VPCs, security groups, and zero-trust network access solutions;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Manage identity and access management (IAM) policies, service control policies, and least privilege frameworks;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Monitor and respond to cloud security events using CloudTrail, GuardDuty, Security Hub, and SIEM integration;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Conduct security assessments of Kubernetes clusters, container registries, and serverless architectures;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with platform and infrastructure teams to harden cloud environments and resolve security findings;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Drive cloud security initiatives including encryption strategies, secrets management, and data protection controls;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Evaluate and integrate cloud-native security tools for runtime protection and threat detection&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;/ul&gt;\n&lt;h4&gt;WHAT WE&#39;RE LOOKING FOR&lt;/h4&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Core Experience&lt;/strong&gt;:&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;ul&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;5+ years as a Security Engineer with 4+ years specialising in cloud security&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Deep AWS security expertise (IAM, VPC, Security Hub, GuardDuty, KMS, CloudTrail, Config)&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Advanced Infrastructure as Code skills (Terraform required, CloudFormation)&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Strong understanding of Kubernetes security (RBAC, network policies, Pod Security Standards)&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Experience with container security tools (Falco, Trivy, etc)&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Proficiency in Python and automation for security policy enforcement&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Knowledge of security frameworks and cloud compliance (ISO 27001, SOC 2, CIS Benchmarks)&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Experience with DevSecOps practices and security integration in CI/CD pipelines&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Understanding of network security, TLS/mTLS, service mesh architectures&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Multi-cloud experience (GCP, Azure) is advantageous&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Knowledge of financial services regulations (MaRisk, BAIT, GDPR) is a plus&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;/ul&gt;\n&lt;h4&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/h4&gt;\n&lt;h4&gt;WHY YOU SHOULD APPLY NOW&lt;/h4&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;Our culture rewards ownership, excellence, and high energy. We care deeply about outcomes and hold each other accountable - we’re here to win and fix one of the largest challenges Europeans face - closing the pension gap and democratising wealth. If this gets you fired up, reach out!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-conclusion&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;We believe it’s our team’s varied identities and backgrounds that make us sharper and stronger. We’re committed to creating an environment where everyone feels respected and has equal opportunity to thrive in their careers. For any questions on DEI during the interview process, reach out to your recruitment partner.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;","departments":[{"id":4029831003,"name":"Information Security","child_ids":[],"parent_id":null}],"offices":[{"id":4024843003,"name":"Berlin","location":"Berlin, Berlin, Germany","child_ids":[],"parent_id":null}]},{"absolute_url":"https://traderepublic.com/en-de/about?jobId=6302030003&gh_jid=6302030003","data_compliance":[{"type":"gdpr","requires_consent":false,"requires_processing_consent":false,"requires_retention_consent":false,"retention_period":null,"demographic_data_consent_applies":