":{"name":"Headquarter"},"metadata":null,"id":5614731003,"updated_at":"2026-02-24T10:10:11-05:00","requisition_id":"803","title":"Senior Technical Product Manager","company_name":"Trade Republic","first_published":"2023-05-15T11:57:52-04:00","language":"en","content":"&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Please note that this position is based in Berlin or London, depending on your availability.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;h4&gt;THE BEST WORK OF YOUR CAREER&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;Trade Republic is the largest savings platform in Europe - we operate in 18 countries, serving +10 million customers who trusted us with over 150B in assets. But we’re striving for more.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;We have a bold mission to empower everyone to build wealth with easy, safe, and free access to financial systems. You will have the opportunity to grow your career by collaborating with a team of outstanding talents and state of the art technology to build a lasting, positive future for millions.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;h4&gt;WHAT YOU&#39;LL BE DOING&lt;/h4&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;We are looking for Product Managers of different seniority levels in several product areas, such as Banking, Cards, Wealth, Fincrime, among others. Your responsibilities will include:&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;ul&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Become the ultimate owner of one or more technical products, taking care of them from a 360 degrees perspective, from ideation to delivery, engineering team management, tracking performance and business impact&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Analyze data to find the right problems to solve, and breaking solutions down into smaller executable chunks that deliver value&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Understand your user and existing state-of-the-art solutions, and create a compelling product vision and roadmap&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Work cross-functionally with engineers and operations managers, and interact security, compliance, data, and legal teams to craft solutions that will delight our users and provide value to the business&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;/ul&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;h4&gt;WHAT WE&#39;RE LOOKING FOR&lt;/h4&gt;\n&lt;ul&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Minimum 4 years of product management hands-on experience in user facing or technical products (i.e. platforms, distributed systems, SDKs, etc.)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Founder-mindset - you enjoy working in highly autonomous, ambiguous and fast paced environment&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Strong analytical, prioritisation, organisational and problem solving skills&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Experience in successfully working with cross-functional teams (engineering, data, security, operations, design&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;/ul&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;h4&gt;WHY YOU SHOULD APPLY NOW&lt;/h4&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;Our culture rewards ownership, excellence, and high energy. We care deeply about outcomes and hold each other accountable - we’re here to win and fix one of the largest challenges Europeans face - closing the pension gap and democratising wealth. If this gets you fired up, reach out!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-conclusion&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;We believe it’s our team’s varied identities and backgrounds that make us sharper and stronger. We’re committed to creating an environment where everyone feels respected and has equal opportunity to thrive in their careers. For any questions on DEI during the interview process, reach out to your recruitment partner.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;","departments":[{"id":4046994003,"name":"Product Management","child_ids":[],"parent_id":4027963003}],"offices":[{"id":4024843003,"name":"Berlin","location":"Berlin, Berlin, Germany","child_ids":[],"parent_id":null},{"id":4074610003,"name":"London","location":"London, England, United Kingdom","child_ids":[],"parent_id":null},{"id":4077193003,"name":"Paris ","location":"Paris, Paris, France","child_ids":[],"parent_id":null}]},{"absolute_url":"https://traderepublic.com/en-de/about?jobId=6551435003&gh_jid=6551435003","data_compliance":[{"type":"gdpr","requires_consent":false,"requires_processing_consent":false,"requires_retention_consent":false,"retention_period":null,"demographic_data_consent_applies":false}],"internal_job_id":4796601003,"location":{"name":"Berlin; London; Paris"},"metadata":null,"id":6551435003,"updated_at":"2026-02-24T10:10:11-05:00","requisition_id":"803","title":"Senior Technical Product Manager - Banking infra","company_name":"Trade Republic","first_published":"2025-04-22T12:15:01-04:00","language":"en","content":"&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Senior Technical Product Manager (Banking Infra)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Please note that this position is based in Berlin, London or Paris, depending on your availability.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;h4&gt;&lt;strong&gt;THE BEST WORK OF YOUR CAREER&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;Trade Republic is the largest savings platform in Europe - we operate in 18 countries, serving +10 million customers who trusted us with over 150B in assets. But we’re striving for more.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;We have a bold mission to empower everyone to build wealth with easy, safe, and free access to financial systems. You will have the opportunity to grow your career by collaborating with a team of outstanding talents and state of the art technology to build a lasting, positive future for millions.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;h4&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHAT YOU&#39;LL BE DOING&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;We are looking for Product Managers of varying seniority levels to join key product areas such as Banking Infrastructure, Cards, Wealth, and Fincrime. As part of the Banking Infrastructure team, you will play a crucial role in shaping and scaling the technological backbone of Trade Republic. The team owns the payment rails, ledger, and core banking platform, all of which are critical to the integrity, performance, and reliability of our financial products.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;Your responsibilities will include:&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;ul&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Take full ownership of core banking components&lt;/strong&gt;: You’ll be the end-to-end owner of one (or more) of our foundational systems such as our core banking platform, payment rails, and ledger. This includes defining the long-term vision, prioritizing initiatives, and ensuring robust execution—from ideation to delivery—while ensuring reliability, scalability, and regulatory compliance.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Drive product development with a 360° mindset&lt;/strong&gt;: Collaborate closely with engineering to shape and deliver high-quality solutions. You’ll be line managing a team of engineers and serve as a strong partner to engineering leadership by bringing a systems-thinking approach, helping navigate technical trade-offs, and keeping delivery aligned with long-term product goals.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Use data to drive decisions&lt;/strong&gt;: Rely on data-driven insights to identify root problems, prioritize what matters most, and break down complex solutions into incremental and measurable product iterations. You’ll define success through clear metrics and KPIs, ensuring alignment with strategic business goals.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Build future-proof systems&lt;/strong&gt;: As the company scales, so must the systems. You will evaluate industry best practices, understand evolving user needs, and design infrastructure that is modular, resilient, and ready for the next stage of growth.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Work cross-functionally at scale&lt;/strong&gt;: Collaborate with a diverse set of stakeholders—including engineering, operations, compliance, security, legal, and data teams—to design solutions that are not only technically sound but also secure, compliant, and operationally viable. You will be the connective tissue between teams, ensuring alignment and clarity.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Act as a thought leader and partner to engineering&lt;/strong&gt;: Serve as a strong partner to engineering leadership by bringing a systems-thinking approach, helping navigate technical trade-offs, and keeping delivery aligned with long-term product goals.&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;/ul&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;WHAT WE&#39;RE LOOKING FOR&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;ul&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Minimum 4 years of product management hands-on experience in user facing or technical products (i.e. platforms, distributed systems, SDKs, etc.)&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Founder-mindset - you enjoy working in highly autonomous, ambiguous and fast paced environment&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Strong analytical, prioritisation, organisational and problem solving skills&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Experience in successfully working with cross-functional teams (engineering, data, security, operations, design&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;/ul&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;h4&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHY YOU SHOULD APPLY NOW&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;\n&lt;ul&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Our culture rewards ownership, excellence, and high energy. We care deeply about outcomes and hold each other accountable - we’re here to win and fix one of the largest challenges Europeans face - closing the pension gap and democratising wealth. If this gets you fired up, reach out!&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;We believe it’s our team’s varied identities and backgrounds that make us sharper and stronger. We’re committed to creating an environment where everyone feels respected and has equal opportunity to thrive in their careers.&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-conclusion&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;We believe it’s our team’s varied identities and backgrounds that make us sharper and stronger. We’re committed to creating an environment where everyone feels respected and has equal opportunity to thrive in their careers. For any questions on DEI during the interview process, reach out to your recruitment partner.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;","departments":[{"id":4046994003,"name":"Product Management","child_ids":[],"parent_id":4027963003}],"offices":[{"id":4024843003,"name":"Berlin","location":"Berlin, Berlin, Germany","child_ids":[],"parent_id":null},{"id":4074610003,"name":"London","location":"London, England, United Kingdom","child_ids":[],"parent_id":null},{"id":4077193003,"name":"Paris ","location":"Paris, Paris, France","child_ids":[],"parent_id":null}]},{"absolute_url":"https://traderepublic.com/en-de/about?jobId=7653497003&gh_jid=7653497003","data_compliance":[{"type":"gdpr","requires_consent":false,"requires_processing_consent":false,"requires_retention_consent":false,"retention_period":null,"demographic_data_consent_applies":false}],"internal_job_id":5727473003,"location":{"name":"Headquarter"},"metadata":null,"id":7653497003,"updated_at":"2026-03-06T08:36:35-05:00","requisition_id":"1197","title":"Social Media Manager","company_name":"Trade Republic","first_published":"2026-03-06T08:35:44-05:00","language":"en","content":"&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Please note that this position is based in Berlin, Germany - relocation support is provided if required.&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;h3&gt;THE BEST WORK OF YOUR CAREER&lt;/h3&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;Trade Republic is the largest savings platform in Europe - we operate in 18 countries, serving +10 million customers who trusted us with over 150B in assets. But we’re striving for more.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;We have a bold mission to empower everyone to build wealth with easy, safe, and free access to financial systems. You will have the opportunity to grow your career by collaborating with a team of outstanding talents and state of the art technology to build a lasting, positive future for millions.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHAT YOU’LL BE DOING&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;We believe social media isn’t just a marketing channel. It&#39;s how we build a community that carries our brand into culture. Our mission is that finance should be accessible, understandable, and part of everyday conversations. As a Social Media Manager, you’ll play a key role in shaping how millions engage with that mission online. How they learn and talk about finances, normalising the exchange.&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Your responsibilities will include:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;ul&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Create scroll-stopping content that makes people laugh, think, share and actually care about their money&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Spot trends faster than the algorithm and know exactly how to twist them to fit our world of banking, putting Trade Republic top of mind. Always culturally relevant and with Zeitgeist. You transcreate, knowing your leeway between creativity and compliance&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Jump from brainstorming ideas to filming, editing, and hitting publish. You love getting your hands dirty and have a bias to action&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Understands Wall Street lingo, but refuses to use it. We break barriers and know how to easily communicate the seemingly most complex topics&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Build and nurture our community, because meaningful conversations drive culture (and yes, organic growth)&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;/ul&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHAT WE&#39;RE LOOKING FOR&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;We’re after someone who navigates the online world easily and with great confidence. And also gets the bigger picture of why people should talk about finance at brunch.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;ul&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;You have at least 2 years of experience managing social media accounts, either for a company or your own channels&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;You eat trends for breakfast and understand what makes a post go viral (and what makes people roll their eyes)&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;You’re a bit of a finance nerd, or at least curious enough to turn complex stuff into something your friends actually get&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;You believe community management isn’t a chore; it’s where culture happens&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;You’re fluent in both English and German, and you can switch tones as effortlessly as switching tabs. French is a plus&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;/ul&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHY YOU SHOULD APPLY NOW&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;Our culture rewards ownership, excellence, and high energy. We care deeply about outcomes and hold each other accountable - we’re here to win and fix one of the largest challenges Europeans face - closing the pension gap and democratising wealth. If this gets you fired up, reach out!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-conclusion&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;We believe it’s our team’s varied identities and backgrounds that make us sharper and stronger. We’re committed to creating an environment where everyone feels respected and has equal opportunity to thrive in their careers. For any questions on DEI during the interview process, reach out to your recruitment partner.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;","departments":[{"id":4057653003,"name":"Growth","child_ids":[4057656003,4026478003,4057654003,4064610003,4057655003,4064611003],"parent_id":null}],"offices":[{"id":4024843003,"name":"Berlin","location":"Berlin, Berlin, Germany","child_ids":[],"parent_id":null}]},{"absolute_url":"https://traderepublic.com/en-de/about?jobId=7648847003&gh_jid=7648847003","data_compliance":[{"type":"gdpr","requires_consent":false,"requires_processing_consent":false,"requires_retention_consent":false,"retention_period":null,"demographic_data_consent_applies":false}],"internal_job_id":5725538003,"location":{"name":"Headquarter"},"metadata":null,"id":7648847003,"updated_at":"2026-03-04T04:43:00-05:00","requisition_id":"1194","title":"Tax Manager - Product Taxes - Germany ","company_name":"Trade Republic","first_published":"2026-03-04T04:43:00-05:00","language":"en","content":"&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Please note that this position is based in Berlin, Germany - relocation support is provided if required.&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;h3&gt;THE BEST WORK OF YOUR CAREER&lt;/h3&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;Trade Republic is the largest savings platform in Europe - we operate in 18 countries, serving +10 million customers who trusted us with over 150B in assets. But we’re striving for more.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;We have a bold mission to empower everyone to build wealth with easy, safe, and free access to financial systems. You will have the opportunity to grow your career by collaborating with a team of outstanding talents and state of the art technology to build a lasting, positive future for millions.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHAT YOU’LL BE DOING&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;ul&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;You will be the subject matter expert for tax topics that relate to the entire product range of Trade Republic: securities, crypto, current accounts, cards and more, with focus on Germany as the main tax jurisdictions. You will also own the coordination of the Austrian tax jurisdiction.&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Work closely with our Product, Operations and Growth teams to enable the development of financial products and related tax topics.&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Own product tax topics for our international markets, supporting as a tax expert to enable our growth strategy beyond Germany.&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Drive tax changes, improvements and requirements: frontend to backend.&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Ensure compliance with local tax reporting requirements, for customers and tax authorities. &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Coordinate with our external partners, including financial institutions, service providers and tax advisors.&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Analyze existing and upcoming tax laws regarding their impact on Trade Republic’s existing and future business and take responsibility for necessary implementation.&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;/ul&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHAT WE&#39;RE LOOKING FOR&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\n&lt;ul&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;You don&#39;t need to be a capital markets tax expert, we are looking for someone who has a professional tax background and is willing to deep dive into everything tax - with a passion for capital markets. &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Experience in the financial services / banking sector is a plus.&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Strong communicator with the ability to effectively collaborate with internal and external stakeholders, clearly articulate complex tax topics succinctly.&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;German and English language skills are required (full professional proficiency).&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;/ul&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHY YOU SHOULD APPLY NOW&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;Our culture rewards ownership, excellence, and high energy. We care deeply about outcomes and hold each other accountable - we’re here to win and fix one of the largest challenges Europeans face - closing the pension gap and democratising wealth. If this gets you fired up, reach out!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-conclusion&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;We believe it’s our team’s varied identities and backgrounds that make us sharper and stronger. We’re committed to creating an environment where everyone feels respected and has equal opportunity to thrive in their careers. For any questions on DEI during the interview process, reach out to your recruitment partner.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;","departments":[{"id":4026449003,"name":"Finance","child_ids":[4026455003,4047035003,4047034003,4047036003,4026450003],"parent_id":null}],"offices":[{"id":4024843003,"name":"Berlin","location":"Berlin, Berlin, Germany","child_ids":[],"parent_id":null}]},{"absolute_url":"https://traderepublic.com/en-de/about?jobId=7659553003&gh_jid=7659553003","data_compliance":[{"type":"gdpr","requires_consent":false,"requires_processing_consent":false,"requires_retention_consent":false,"retention_period":null,"demographic_data_consent_applies":false}],"internal_job_id":5729915003,"location":{"name":"Headquarter"},"metadata":null,"id":7659553003,"updated_at":"2026-03-16T12:10:12-04:00","requisition_id":"1199","title":"Tax Transformation & Operations Intern / Working Student","company_name":"Trade Republic","first_published":"2026-03-16T12:10:12-04:00","language":"en","content":"&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Please note that this position is based in Berlin, Germany.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;h3&gt;THE BEST WORK OF YOUR CAREER&lt;/h3&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;Trade Republic is the largest savings platform in Europe - we operate in 18 countries, serving +10 million customers who trusted us with over 150B in assets. But we’re striving for more.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;We have a bold mission to empower everyone to build wealth with easy, safe, and free access to financial systems. You will have the opportunity to grow your career by collaborating with a team of outstanding talents and state of the art technology to build a lasting, positive future for millions.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHAT YOU’LL BE DOING&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;ul&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Active involvement in tax compliance (e.g., CIT and VAT returns) where you will go beyond data entry: You will learn to ensure data integrity and connect the dots between tax reporting, the P&amp;amp;L, and the balance sheet to understand the broader financial impact on our business.&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Assist in the digital transformation of tax processes, including SAP optimization and the implementation of automated tax reporting tools.&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Ensure high-quality tax data by conducting monthly tax checks and supporting the Internal Tax Compliance Management System (TCMS).&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Help to design, track and visualize Tax KPIs to enhance strategic decision-making.&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Analyse existing and upcoming tax laws regarding their impact on Trade Republic’s existing and future business.&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Drive innovation by screening and evaluating new digitization tools and AI use cases to continuously improve our internal work methods.&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;/ul&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHAT WE&#39;RE LOOKING FOR&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;ul&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Academic background in Business, Law, or Economics with a clear focus on Taxation (e.g., specialized tax modules or initial internship experience)&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Strong affinity for numbers and the motivation to learn how to translate complex tax data into clear reports&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Proficient Microsoft Excel knowledge and an AI native mindset, familiarity with SAP is